【 成长 的 烦恼 讲解 版 】 220



想 看看 小 Ben 拍 的 家庭 打扫 日 的 Video 吗 ？
想 知道 ， Jason 一家 又 出 了 什么 好玩 的 事 吗 ？
呵呵 ， 来 看看 下面 的 片断 吧 。



要求 ： 每次 ， 我们 只 听   2 ,   3   分钟 左右 ， 然后 把 序号 标出 的 缺词 填好 即可

Ben :     Tick     tick   tick   tick .   Hi   this   is   sixty   minutes .   But   it   won ' t
worry .     It   will   not   take   that   long . Hi ,   I ’ m   Ben   seaver ,   and   welcome   to
my     class     * * 1 * * .   A   day   in   the   life   of   the   Seavers .   And   what   a   day     it
is ?     It ’ s     chore     day     and   everybody   has   a   job   to   do .   Mrs .   Seaver   and
Carol     are   going   to   clean   the   drapes ,   and   Doctor   seaver ' s   using   carols
computor     to   write   some   article   for   some   * * 2 * *   magazine .   Oh   yeah ,   he ' s
a     psychiatrist .     And     Mike ' s   gotta   paint   his   room ,   or   dads   gonna   know
the     reason     why .     I     don ' t   even   care   what   grade   I   get   on   this .   I   just
want   to   do   A   good   job   for   you   Mrs .   Cutter .
Jenny :   Ben ,   you   were   supposed   to   mention   me .
Ben :     Ok ,     ok .     Jenny     Foster ,     another     one   of   your   fine   students ,   is
helping   me   by   * * 3 * *   the   video   camera .
Jenny :   Hi   Mrs .   Cutter .
Ben :     Well ,   one   thing   you ' re ... one   thing   you   are   going   to   notice   about
the   Seavers ,   is   how   well   we   get   along .
Maggie :   Come   on   Jason .
Jason :   Maggie ,   threes   a   difference   between   frugal   and   cheap .
Maggie :   Ok ,   I   take   it   back .   You ' re   a   frugal - skate .
Jason :     Well ,     I     don ' t     see     what ’ s     wrong     with   going   with   the   old ,
reliable ,   inexpensive   handy   man   we ' ve   always   used   for   years .
Maggie :     Honey ,     a     furnace     is     not     a     broken     screen     door .     It ' s   a
complicated   piece   of   machinery .
Jason :     Well ,     I   think   jimmy   can   handle   it .   And   did   I   mention   he   works
cheap ?
Maggie :   Would   you   hire   him   to   perform   open   heart   * * 4 * * ?
Jason :   Well   I ’ d   let   him   give   me   an   estimate .
Maggie :   Ben ,   Jenny ,   not   now ,   please .
Ben :   Keep   rolling ,   this   could   be   good .
Maggie :   Honey ,   you   know   I   love   dear   sweet   jimmy   as   much   as   you   and   the
kids   do .
Jason :   of   course .   So   why   not   destroy   the   man ' s   * * 5 * * ?
Maggie :   Ha !
Ben :     It     may     look     like   they ' re   arguing ,   but   they   are   not .   They   call
this   discussing .
Maggie :   Ben ,   I   told   you   to   turn   that   off .
Jason :   No ,   keep   rolling   Ben .   This   could   be   great   stuff .
Maggie :   Ben   I   am   not   going   to   ask   you   again .
Ben :     Uh     oh !   It   looks   like   I   have   been   invited   to   participate   in   this
discussion .

TIPS :

1 .   chore   家庭 杂务
chore   day 就是 我们 常说 的 “ 大扫除 日 ”
让 我们 再 来 看看 chore 的 其他 用法
chore   around 作 短工 ； 作 临时工
chore   boy 干 杂活 的 临时 工人 , 跑腿 的 人

2 .   frugal - skate   小气鬼 ， 吝啬鬼
frugal   adj . 节俭 的 ,   朴素 的
skate 除了 可以 表示 滑冰 ， 滑冰鞋 以外
还 可以 用来 表示 人
与 什么样 的 形容词 搭配 就 可以 表示 不同 的 人
比如 ： cheap   skate 就是 吝啬鬼 ;   卑鄙 的 人
good   skate 就是 讨人喜欢 的 人

3 .   I   am   not   going   to   ask   you   again
这句 话 什么 意思 呢 ？
这里 的 ask 可不是 问 的 意思 哦
这句 话 Maggie 想 说 的 其实 是 ：
I   don ' t   want   to   say   it   again .
I   don ' t   want   to   mention   it   twice .



KEY :

1 .   project
2 .   mental
3 .   running
4 .   surgery
5 .   dignity
